00:33:31.926 --> 00:33:32.986 A:middle
What's the audience of this

00:33:32.986 --> 00:33:33.556 A:middle
page?

00:33:34.716 --> 00:33:35.656 A:middle
Is it advanced?

00:33:36.116 --> 00:33:39.266 A:middle
Beginner? Are they science

00:33:39.326 --> 00:33:39.796 A:middle
students?

00:33:40.206 --> 00:33:40.966 A:middle
Are they artists?

00:33:42.086 --> 00:33:42.866 A:middle
The way you're going to figure

00:33:42.866 --> 00:33:44.326 A:middle
that out is, you have your

00:33:44.326 --> 00:33:46.046 A:middle
target audience in mind, and

00:33:46.046 --> 00:33:47.536 A:middle
then you need to do user

00:33:47.536 --> 00:33:48.206 A:middle
testing.

00:33:48.646 --> 00:33:49.986 A:middle
Find out if this is too

