be explained more, or perhaps

00:33:56.766 --> 00:33:56.916 A:middle
less.

00:33:57.666 --> 00:33:58.706 A:middle
Don't underestimate your

00:33:58.706 --> 00:33:58.976 A:middle
audience either.

