to some of my co-workers in the

00:34:40.806 --> 00:34:40.996 A:middle
office.

00:34:41.556 --> 00:34:43.045 A:middle
Hey, Alex, does this make any

00:34:43.045 --> 00:34:43.626 A:middle
sense to you?

