00:35:13.396 --> 00:35:15.296 A:middle
Passion is so important.

00:35:16.586 --> 00:35:17.556 A:middle
This should be threaded

00:35:17.556 --> 00:35:18.736 A:middle
throughout all your other

00:35:18.736 --> 00:35:20.136 A:middle
playground prototyping and

00:35:20.136 --> 00:35:20.696 A:middle
thinking.

00:35:21.486 --> 00:35:22.646 A:middle
Why are you even doing this?

00:35:22.646 --> 00:35:23.506 A:middle
Why are you writing a

00:35:23.506 --> 00:35:24.176 A:middle
playground?

00:35:24.766 --> 00:35:25.976 A:middle
It's because you're passionate

00:35:25.976 --> 00:35:27.076 A:middle
about something that you want to

00:35:27.076 --> 00:35:28.676 A:middle
share, that you want to teach to

00:35:28.676 --> 00:35:29.316 A:middle
someone else.

00:35:30.746 --> 00:35:31.946 A:middle
If you're not passionate about

00:35:31.946 --> 00:35:33.026 A:middle
what you're writing a playground

00:35:33.026 --> 00:35:34.396 A:middle
about, why are you doing it?

00:35:34.396 --> 00:35:37.966 A:middle
And that, that not passion is

00:35:37.966 --> 00:35:39.406 A:middle
going to show through, and your

00:35:39.406 --> 00:35:40.766 A:middle
learner's not care either.

00:35:41.426 --> 00:35:42.696 A:middle
So, bringing your passion to

00:35:42.696 --> 00:35:44.246 A:middle
this is so important.

00:35:44.746 --> 00:35:46.536 A:middle
How can you do this?

00:35:47.596 --> 00:35:49.436 A:middle
Well, let's take a look at the

