This appeals to a lot of people.

00:36:19.456 --> 00:36:20.896 A:middle
Gets them excited about jumping

00:36:20.896 --> 00:36:21.866 A:middle
into this world and writing

00:36:21.866 --> 00:36:21.956 A:middle
code.

